.TH MAC-SETUP 7 "2026-03-12" "mac-setup" "Tom's System Reference"
.SH NAME
mac-setup \- opinionated macOS bootstrap with Homebrew, Stow, and Catppuccin Mocha
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./setup.sh
.RI [ \-\-dry\-run ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Idempotent macOS bootstrap that installs packages via Homebrew, manages
dotfiles with GNU Stow, installs runtimes with mise, and applies
Catppuccin Mocha theming across all tools.
.PP
The repo lives at
.B ~/Workspace/mac-setup
and can be re-run safely at any time.
.SH BOOTSTRAP STEPS
.IP 1. 4
Install Xcode Command Line Tools and accept license
.IP 2. 4
Install Homebrew
.IP 3. 4
Install packages/apps from Brewfile (gcloud-cli and docker-desktop deferred)
.IP 4. 4
Create .env from .env.example if missing
.IP 5. 4
Back up existing configs to ~/config-backups/
.IP 6. 4
Stow dotfiles into $HOME
.IP 7. 4
Install private fonts from iCloud Drive
.IP 8. 4
Prompt for git user.name and user.email (stored in ~/.gitconfig.local)
.IP 9. 4
Generate SSH key (ed25519) if missing; upload to GitHub via gh
.IP 10. 4
Verify git commit signing (1Password SSH agent, signing key)
.IP 11. 4
Install Ghostty shaders, link macOS app configs (Zed, Obsidian)
.IP 12. 4
Install LazyVim, stow Neovim plugin configs, download zjstatus
.IP 13. 4
Install runtimes via mise (node, python, ruby, go)
.IP 14. 4
Install gcloud-cli, Docker Desktop, App Store apps
.IP 15. 4
Install Rust via rustup-init and Cargo tools (basalt-tui) via cargo-binstall
.IP 16. 4
Prune old backups in ~/config-backups/, keeping the 3 most recent
.SH STOW PACKAGES
Each package under
.B stow/
mirrors $HOME structure.
Re-stow with:
.B (cd stow && stow \-\-target="$HOME" \-\-restow <package>)
.PP
.TS
l l.
Package	Contents
_
zsh	.zshrc, .zprofile
git	.gitconfig, .gitignore (global)
bat	.config/bat/config
lazygit	.config/lazygit/config.yml
ripgrep	.ripgreprc
ssh	.ssh/config (1Password agent, Include config.local)
starship	.config/starship.toml
ghostty	.config/ghostty/config
zellij	.config/zellij/config.kdl, layouts/default.kdl, scripts/
mise	.config/mise/config.toml
zed	.config/zed/settings.json
nvim	.config/nvim/lua/config/options.lua, plugins/ghostty.lua
obsidian	.config/obsidian/obsidian.json
claude	.claude/CLAUDE.md, skills/, statusline.sh
eza	.config/eza/theme.yml
yazi	.config/yazi/theme.toml, Catppuccin-mocha.tmTheme
skhd	.config/skhd/skhdrc (Hyper key app launchers)
karabiner	.config/karabiner/assets/complex_modifications/hyper.json
.TE
