.SH SHELL OPTIONS
.TP
.B auto_cd
Type a directory name to cd into it (e.g.,
.B ../foo
instead of
.BR "cd ../foo" ).
.TP
.B extended_glob
Advanced glob patterns (#, ~, ^).
.TP
.B correct
Suggests corrections for mistyped commands.
.TP
.B append_history
Append to history file instead of overwriting.
.TP
.B share_history
Share history across all open shells.
.TP
.B hist_ignore_dups
Skip duplicate history entries.
.TP
.B hist_ignore_space
Commands starting with a space are not recorded.
.TP
.B hist_reduce_blanks
Remove superfluous blanks from history entries.
